{{hy-conj-ել|mp=on}}: {{hy-conj-ել|ծծ|mp=on|caus=on|note=in the sense of blowjob the causative is always the colloquial {{m|hy|ծծցնել}}}}

{{hy-conj-ել|աս||աս|imp1=[[ասա՛]]|imp2=[[ասե՛ք]]*, [[ասացե՛ք]]|prohib1=[[մի՛]] [[ասա]]|prohib2=[[մի՛]] [[ասեք]]*, [[մի՛]] [[ասացեք]]|aor=ասաց|mp=on|note=*Note the unexpected aorist stem {{m|hy||ասաց-}}, inherited from Old Armenian: see {{m|xcl|ասեմ}}. It should be mentioned though, that colloquially the regular stem {{m|hy||ասեց-}} is used: {{m|hy|ասեցի}}, {{m|hy|ասեցիր}}, {{m|hy|ասեց}}, {{m|hy|ասեցինք}}, {{m|hy|ասեցիք}}, {{m|hy|ասեցին}}
{{hy-conj-ել|տան||տար|imp1=[[տա՛ր]]|prohib1=[[մի՛]] [[տար]]|pass=[[տարվել]]|note=note the irregular aorist stem and the imperative}}
{{hy-conj-ալ|լվան||լվաց|imp1=[[լվա՛]]|prohib1=[[մի՛]] [[լվա]]|aor=լվաց|caus=on|note=note the irregularity in aorist, which is conjugated with the help of corresponding forms of {{m|hy|լվալ|}}

{{hy-conj-ալ|երթ||գնաց|imp1=[[երթա՛]]|prohib1=[[մի՛]] [[երթա]]|aor=գնաց|note=this is a [[suppletion|suppletive]] verb, which means part of the conjugation is filled by forms of another verb, namely by {{m|hy|գնալ}}}}

{{hy-conj-ալ|էթ||գնաց|imp1=[[էթա՛]]|prohib1=[[մի՛]] [[էթա]]|aor=գնաց|note=this is a [[suppletion|suppletive]] verb, which means the part of the conjugation is filled by forms of another verb, namely by {{m|hy|գնալ|}}}}

{{hy-conj-ել|թողն||թող|imp1=[[թո՛ղ]]|prohib1=[[մի՛]] [[թող]]|aor=թողեց|note=note the irregularity in the aorist which is conjugated as if this verb were not suffixed; for difference, compare the conjugation of another suffixed verb: {{m|hy|մտնել}}
{{hy-conj-ալ|բառն||բարձ|aor=բարձեց|note=note how the aorist stem changes to {{m|hy||բարձ-}}; see etymology of Old Armenian {{m|xcl|բառնամ}} for explanation}}

{{hy-conj-ալ|կեն||կաց|imp1=[[կա՛ց]], [[կացի՛ր]], [[կացի՛]]*|prohib1=[[մի՛]] [[կաց]], [[մի՛]] [[կացիր]], [[մի՛]] [[կացի]]*|caus=on|note=note how the aorist changes to {{m|hy|կաց-}}{{hy-conj-ալ|կեն||կեց|imp1=[[կա՛ց]], [[կացի՛ր]], [[կացի՛]]*|prohib1=[[մի՛]] [[կաց]], [[մի՛]] [[կացիր]], [[մի՛]] [[կացի]]*|caus=on|note=note how the aorist changes to {{m|hy|կեց-}}

{{hy-conj-ալ|բան|note=The forms of indicative present and imperfect mentioned above are rarely used to avoid confusion with identical forms of {{m|hy|բանել||to work}}. Instead {{m|hy|բացել}} or {{m|hy|բաց անել}} are used.}}
